702125f-c.title: Bronx: Westchester Avenue - Seabury Avenue
702125f-c.text:
(1)
Westchester Avenue (elevated thereon), at the S.W. corner of
Seabury Avenue, showing St. Peters Protestant Episcopal Church.
The view is southwestward from the downtown platform of the West-
chester Square elevated station of the I.R.T. Peiham Bay Park
subway line.
July 1, 1928
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(2) A view of the church across Seabury Avenue.
July 1, 1928
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
(3)
A view of the church as seen eastward along Westchester
Avenue from Herschel Street.
July 1, 1928
P. L. Sperr
NO REPRODUCTIONS
